# Class: <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Security> (Security)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Security> "Contains all the Security related Classes")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#Security> "Security"@en)
